" Tabs
map <S-j> gT
map <S-k> gt

" Splits
map <C-h> <C-w>h
map <C-j> <C-w>j
map <C-k> <C-w>k
map <C-l> <C-w>l

" Save
nmap <C-s> <Esc>:w<CR>
vmap <C-s> <Esc>:w<CR>
imap <C-s> <Esc>:w<CR>

" Quit
nmap <C-q> <Esc>:q!<CR>
vmap <C-q> <Esc>:q!<CR>
imap <C-q> <Esc>:q!<CR>

" Copy
vmap <C-c> "*y<CR>
imap <C-c> <Esc>"*y<CR>
nmap <C-c> "*y<CR>

vmap <C-p> "*p<CR>
imap <C-p> <Esc>"*p<CR>
nmap <C-p> "*p<CR>
